
@COM1000
;母乳分泌促進薬

SELECTCOM = 1000
LOSEBASE:体力 += 30
LOSEBASE:气力 += 30
SOURCE:Ｎ疼痛 = 1000
SOURCE:耻辱 = 1000
SOURCE:屈辱 = 1000
SOURCE:支配 = 600
SOURCE:已用时间 = 1
SOURCE:选择指令口上隐藏 = 1
EXP:肉体改造 ++
SETBIT ＃有效药品／母乳分泌促进药＃
ITEM:母乳分泌促进药 --
CALL BUST_TENTACLE_RESET
TRYCALLFORM COM{SELECTCOM}_MESSAGE
RETURN 1



